I was very unhappy to hear that tonight will be the only time I will have food delivered to my home from Green Cactus Grill in Huntington Village.  Due to their inability to hire a delivery person at the Huntington, Jericho Tpke location and my delivery location being closer to this branch the  staff from the Huntington Village location notified me they are unable to deliver food in the future.  I expressed to them that I just wanted to order food and noticing on the web that this branch delivers being in the same town it dawns on me why wouldn't they want to deliver?  They mentioned that it would take away business from the village if deliveries were made closer to the jericho tpke in huntington branch.  I responded that they do not have delivery available and that is why I called them.  I will reconsider my business with Green Cactus Grill and will definitely mention this experience to others.
